# Prisma & Database

**Source of truth:** `apps/api/prisma/schema.prisma`

## Model template
```prisma
model MenuItem {
  id        String   @id @default(dbgenerated("gen_random_uuid()")) @db.Uuid
  nameEn    String   @map("name_en")
  nameAr    String   @map("name_ar")
  isActive  Boolean  @default(true) @map("is_active")
  createdAt DateTime @default(now()) @map("created_at") @db.Timestamptz(6)
  updatedAt DateTime @updatedAt @map("updated_at") @db.Timestamptz(6)
  @@map("menu_items")
}
```

## Naming
- Model: PascalCase · Field: camelCase + `@map("snake_case")` · Table: `@@map("plural_snake")`
- Enums for roles/statuses · Bilingual: `nameEn`/`nameAr` pairs
- `@@index` on FKs and filters (`venueId`, `status`)

## Migrations
1. Edit schema → `npm run migrate:dev` → commit schema + `prisma/migrations/`
2. Prod/CI: `npm run migrate` · After pull: `npm run db:generate`
3. Never edit applied migration SQL

## Seed
`apps/api/src/db/seed.js` — dev only, use `prisma.*.upsert`

